description: Try our easy to follow Fish Cakes recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Fish Cakes Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 3 kaffir lime leaves, spine removed, finely shredded

recipeInstructions.text: Grease and line a tray. Place fish, curry paste and fish sauce in a food processor. Process until finely chopped. Transfer to a bowl with prawn meat, beans, lime leaves and coriander. Stir to combine.
Heat oil in a frying pan over medium heat. Drop spoonfuls of mixture into pan and flatten. Cook, in batches, turning, for 5 minutes or until golden and cooked through.
To make sauce, stir vinegar and sugar together in a bowl until sugar dissolves. Add cucumber, chilli and fish sauce. Stir to combine. Serve fish cakes with dipping sauce and coriander.
